devdoc.title: ZorroController: The main controller of the Zorro yield farming protocol. Used for cash flow operations (deposit/withdrawal), managing vaults, and rewards allocations, among other things.

add(uint256,address,bool,address).notice: Adds a new pool. Can only be called by the owner.

checkXChainDepositFee(uint256,bytes,uint.notice: Checks to see how much a cross chain deposit will cost

checkXChainDistributeEarningsFee(uint256.notice: Checks to see how much a cross chain earnings distribution will cost

checkXChainWithdrawalFee(uint256,uint256.notice: Checks to see how much a cross chain withdrawal will cost

deposit(uint256,uint256,uint256).notice: Deposit Want tokens to associated Vault

depositFullService(uint256,uint256,uint2.notice: Deposits funds in a full service manner (performs autoswaps and obtains Want tokens)

getTimeMultiplier(uint256).notice: Calculate time multiplier based on duration committed

getUserContribution(uint256,uint256).notice: The contribution of the user, meant to be used in rewards allocations

inCaseTokensGetStuck(address,uint256).notice: For owner to recover ERC20 tokens on this contract if stuck

massUpdatePools().notice: Updates reward variables of all pools

pendingZORRORewards(uint256,address,int2.notice: View function to see pending ZORRO on frontend.

poolLength().notice: Number of pools in the Zorro protocol

receiveXChainDepositRequest(uint256,uint.notice: Dummy func to allow .selector call above and guarantee typesafety for abi calls.

receiveXChainDistributionRequest(uint256.notice: Dummy func to allow .selector call above and guarantee typesafety for abi calls.

receiveXChainRepatriationRequest(uint256.notice: Dummy func to allow .selector call above and guarantee typesafety for abi calls.

receiveXChainWithdrawalRequest(uint256,b.notice: Dummy func to allow .selector call above and guarantee typesafety for abi calls.

sendXChainDepositRequest(uint256,uint256.notice: Prepares and sends a cross chain deposit request. Takes care of necessary financial ops (transfer/locking USDC)

sendXChainDistributeEarningsRequest(uint.notice: Sends a request back to the home chain to distribute earnings

sendXChainWithdrawalRequest(uint256,byte.notice: Prepares and sends a cross chain withdrwal request.

set(uint256,uint256,bool).notice: Update the given pool's ZORRO allocation point. Can only be called by the owner.

setZorroPerBlock(uint256,uint256,uint256.notice: Set the number of Zorro to emit per block based on current market parameters

stakedWantTokens(uint256,address,int256).notice: View function to see staked Want tokens on frontend.

trancheLength(uint256,address).notice: Number of tranches invested by a given user into a given pool

transferInvestment(uint256,uint256,uint2.notice: Transfer all assets from a tranche in one vault to a new vault (works on-chain only)

updatePool(uint256).notice: Update reward variables of the given pool to be up-to-date.

withdraw(uint256,uint256,bool).notice: Fully withdraw Want tokens from underlying Vault.

withdrawAll(uint256).notice: Withdraw the maximum number of Want tokens from a pool

withdrawalFullService(uint256,uint256,bo.notice: Withdraws funds from a pool and converts the Want token into USDC
